data.meta_description:
This DVD features the romantic comedy "Must Love Dogs" starring John Cusack and Diane Lane. It is rated PG-13 and comes in a tall/DVD case. The movie is in English and has a region code of DVD: 1 (US, Canada...). The edition is full screen and was released in 2005.


The film follows a woman named Sarah, played by Diane Lane, as she navigates the world of online dating. Along the way, she meets a man named Jake, played by John Cusack, who is also trying to find love online. The movie is a heartwarming story about the ups and downs of modern dating and the importance of having a furry companion by your side.
